data.description: Recently renovated 3-bedroom ranch with finished basement, newer vinyl siding & carport! Stylish kitchen offers new shaker-style cabinets, granite countertops, and top-notch black stainless steel appliances, including fridge, dishwasher, microwave(as-is), and gas stove. Fresh laminate vinyl flooring, and sliders leading to a party sized deck along with fully fenced in spacious backyard. Gorgeous oak hardwood floors, thermal tilt-out windows, and all rooms painted neutral colors. The bathroom features ceramic tile, updated vanity, mirror, lighting, and stunning glass inlay design in the tiled bath surround. Heated lower level with new carpet, built-in bar, and workshop adds over 500 sq ft of living space. Newer washer/dryer included. Architectural roof, efficient gas heating, brand new water heater in 2023 (central AC needs service was not used in 2023) . Prime location near Reed Park, easy access to 91 N&S, and Bradley International Airport. Showing is winning – come check it out! More photos coming soon, viewings begin on 2/24.
